org.forgerock.openam.oauth2.resources.labels

Class UmaLabelsStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openam.oauth2.resources.labels.UmaLabelsStore

  • public class UmaLabelsStore
extends Object
    This class stores and gives access to UMA Resource Set labels. The underlying data is accessed using the DJ LDAP SDK.

        Creates the provided ResourceSetLabel in the database, and returns an instance with the ResourceSetLabel.id field populated with the value used.
        Parameters:
        realm - The current realm.
        username - The user that owns the label.
